data.description: Beautiful Sheryl home located in a cul-de-sac. This spacious home boasts an expansive open concept design, adorned with stunning wood flooring and crown molding. The abundance of windows allows for ample natural light to permeate throughout the interior. The kitchen is equipped with a convenient island, complete with a sink, dishwasher, and additional seating options. The bedrooms are generously proportioned, ensuring comfortable living. Notable upgrades include undercounter lighting, a gas stove, stainless steel appliances, custom maple cabinetry, a primary closet laundry pass-thru, a pantry closet, a covered patio, and a privacy fenced yard with a corner lot concrete curb. Please schedule your showing today!
